Revision history for Win32::LongPath

1.0 September 19, 2013
	- Official release.

0.04 September 5, 2013
	- Fixed bug when stat () a file > 2 ^ 31 bytes.

0.03 August 26, 2013
	- Fixed bug when stat () a file > 2 ^ 32 bytes.

0.02 August 6, 2013
	- Fixed bugs caused by PerlCritic adjustments.

0.01 August 6, 2013
	- First release.
